Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雇佣我们杀你的人
