Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是和情人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,察觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  要杀你的人就是你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失态啊  春寺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟然会被自己养的狗反咬一口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  万一有什么情况  把他处理掉就行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  若是带着入巢莳菜逃走的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来自草花12的紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现9029
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在跟踪中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,位置在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正从港区新桥二丁目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乌森神社往汐留方向徒步移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入巢莳菜呢  和他在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似在单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先不要鲁莽刺激他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追查出他们的潜伏地点才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把他抓来审问就能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方可是9029
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,草花12失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧让周围的人进行增援
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  委托人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是让我去杀同班同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这傻女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别太得寸进尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这任务接与不接  现在立刻回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不接的话如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你直接关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我的回答是  YES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明智的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情况之后会联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  9029保持通常状态进入准待机模式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红心9失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑桃6失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前去增援的王牌一个接一个失去联络
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  你觉得这种做法能长久吗
